Docstring:
Convert data to a (utf-8 encoded) byte-string if it isn't a byte-string
already.
Source body:
```python
    """
    Convert data to a (utf-8 encoded) byte-string if it isn't a byte-string
    already.
    """
    if not isinstance(data, bytes):
        data = str(data).encode("utf-8")
    return data
```

