Find the most efficient mask pattern.
Source body:
```python
        """
        Find the most efficient mask pattern.
        """
        min_lost_point = 0
        pattern = 0

        for i in range(8):
            self.makeImpl(i)

            lost_point = util.lost_point(self.modules)

            if i == 0 or min_lost_point > lost_point:
                min_lost_point = lost_point
                pattern = i

        return pattern
```

