Module: main.py
Signature: def map_data(data, mask_pattern)
Cyclomatic complexity: 11

## Source

Source body:
```python
        inc = -1
        row = self.modules_count - 1
        bitIndex = 7
        byteIndex = 0

        mask_func = util.mask_func(mask_pattern)

        data_len = len(data)

        for col in range(self.modules_count - 1, 0, -2):
            if col <= 6:
                col -= 1  # noqa: PLW2901

            col_range = (col, col - 1)

            while True:
                for c in col_range:
                    if self.modules[row][c] is None:
                        dark = False

                        if byteIndex < data_len:
                            dark = ((data[byteIndex] >> bitIndex) & 1) == 1

                        if mask_func(row, c):
                            dark = not dark

                        self.modules[row][c] = dark
                        bitIndex -= 1

                        if bitIndex == -1:
                            byteIndex += 1
                            bitIndex = 7

                row += inc

                if row < 0 or self.modules_count <= row:
                    row -= inc
                    inc = -inc
                    break
```

